strings:
<voice_0x010013DC><se_high>Red: Oh, 'ere we go... Come to rub me nose in it,
'ave ya? As if I don't feel like enough of a
lemon already.
<voice_0x010013DD><se_high>Red: Well, go on then <endash> 'ave a good laugh.

<voice_0x010013DE><se_low>Yangus: Wot you on about? We got the treasure,
didn't we? An' you ain't even 'urt, neither.
All's well that ends well, innit?

<voice_0x010013DF><se_high>Red: Oh, don't take the 'igh road, Yangus!
Bein' beholden to the likes o' you is bad enough as it is.
<voice_0x010013E0><se_high>Red: Gordon Bennett, I can't 'ardly bear to look at meself in the mirror!
